u0142u\u017cszy czas, przeszed\u0142 ju\u017c faz\u0119 wzrostu. Zachowaj ostro\u017cno\u015b\u0107 w przypadku produkt\u00f3w, kt\u00f3re nadal znajduj\u0105 si\u0119 w tej fazie, gdy\u017c mog\u0105 one utrudnia\u0107 osi\u0105gni\u0119cie rentowno\u015bci.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Podsumowuj\u0105c, skuteczne zarz\u0105dzanie portfelem produkt\u00f3w w kategorii Beauty i FMCG wymaga regularnej analizy oraz elastyczno\u015bci w podejmowaniu decyzji. Wykorzystuj\u0105c powy\u017csze strategie, mo\u017cesz znacz\u0105co poprawi\u0107 rentowno\u015b\u0107 swoich produkt\u00f3w.<\/p>\n<p><b>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<h2>Jak poprawi\u0107 rentowno\u015b\u0107 produkt\u00f3w w kategorii Beauty i FMCG?<\/h2>\n<p>Czy zastanawia\u0142e\u015b si\u0119, jak ef<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":4922,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[2],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4921","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-kontent"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4921"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4921"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4921\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4922"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4921"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.